title: VB6 Help Files Only, Visual Basic 6.0 MSDN
description:
This is the last version of MSDN that supported VB6 (Visual Basic 6).

This is the standard MSDN installation with all help files removed except those for VB6. This trim it down to 50 MB.

If you wish to have help for other Visual Studio 6 products such as Visual C++ 6.0
then you need the full version of MSDN October 2001, which is over 1 GB.

I've created this file for fellow fans of the the best development environment of all time! Please seed!


----- INSTRUCTIONS -----

First, install VB6, select not to install MSDN at the final step.
Unzip this package, run setup.exe.
Choose custom install option.
Select VB Documentation.
Optionally, select VB Product Samples.
You will now have context sensitive help for the IDE and VB6 keywords(press F1 on a keyword or object).
